{"tid":614281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗橫洲井頭村發生火警　大火濃煙直捲半空","createTime":"2018-04-02T11:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T14:57:47.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12276a7f0c3a559f748afed38737d73441b832c4","tid":614281,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"下午4時許，元朗橫洲井頭村發生火警，有一間搭建鐵皮屋起火，一度傳出爆炸聲，濃直捲上半空，警方及消防接報到場，初列一級火警，派出2條喉及2煙帽隊進行灌救，暫未知是否有人傷亡。現場消息稱，起火的鐵皮木屋面積約15米乘15米。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2040000/2042327/aa_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2040000%2F2042327%2Faa_1024.jpg&h=10dd9a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marcus.chiu3/videos/10156098702131427/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarcus.chiu3%2Fvideos%2F10156098702131427%2F&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=93263d5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marcus.chiu3/videos/10156098702131427/</a>"},{"pid":"ff6bdb24747ded8f60ff283ecf6ce376db34dadd","tid":614281,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/826817130843690/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F826817130843690%2F&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ae1a508e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/826817130843690/</a>"}]}